  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：K2-V2-Instruct</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5990740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"696\" data-imgfileid=\"100017096\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c8fab24&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVZnf91jTgHcvKHfIjCDfwTqUEzrHjaUiby1CYcIwRlb1x268Oia2Km3vGlcHTdO9iaSOkdicu4aLSVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★K2-V2-Instruct是LLM360系列中最强大的开源模型之一，采用70B参数的稠密Transformer架构。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型不仅具备标准的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">事实知识</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">对话</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">能力，还展示了强大的长</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">上下文一致性、深度数学理解</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">稳健的推理能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。这些能力为复杂数学问题的解决和Agent工作流的执行等高级下游应用提供了基础。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/k2-v2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/k2-v2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Apriel-1.5</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"630\" data-imgfileid=\"100017097\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2cfac5d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVZnf91jTgHcvKHfIjCDfwlbsu0jSelypvVicO33Tnbnp5u4Ap9cT9e1gvtp9BGlUO0oOibibwFIicBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Apriel-1.5-15b-Thinker 是 ServiceNow 的 Apriel SLM 系列中的多模态推理模型，能够在文本和图像推理任务中实现与体积大十倍的模型相当的性能。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型通过在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">文本和图像领域</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的持续预训练，增强了文本推理能力，并增加了图像推理支持。尽管没有进行图像特定的微调训练，该模型在文本和图像推理任务中均表现出色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/apriel-1-5\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/apriel-1-5</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LightX2V</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3509259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"406\" data-imgfileid=\"100017099\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b27bcd3c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVZnf91jTgHcvKHfIjCDfwtO3brE8PmYXxia3bAWibkWNE7tQ4k4Xy71UeeZVDxxsADn23xCsgl91w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LightX2V 是一个先进的轻量级视频生成推理框架，旨在提供高效的高性能视频合成解决方案</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该平台集成了多种最先进的视频生成技术，支持包括文本到视频（T2V）和图像到视频（I2V）在内的多样化生成任务。X2V 代表将不同的输入模态（如文本或图像）转换为视频输出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lightx2v\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lightx2v</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：ETrajEval</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29814814814814816\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" data-height=\"346\" data-imgfileid=\"100017098\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=66a7fcda&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVZnf91jTgHcvKHfIjCDfww11TC7OiaH2vBcK3CcpwsZzTiaMf2cOHYtOcnPqd4PwmNQ7ibVNlgAlOA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ETrajEval是一个用于评估语言模型中情感支持的官方框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">传统的情感支持评估方法通常依赖于短暂的、静态的对话，评估模型在孤立的“快照”中的响应。这种方法未能捕捉到有效支持的本质，即随着时间的推移适应用户不断变化的情感状态。ETrajEval通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">动态的、以用户为中心的轨迹分析</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来克服这一问题。我们模拟现实的多轮角色扮演场景，其中用户的情感状态受到对话和外部“干扰事件”的影响。我们的框架不仅评估模型产生</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">单一同理心响应</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的能力，还评估其在整个互动过程中持续改善和稳定用户情感健康的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/etrajeval\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/etrajeval</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：CKDA</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47129629629629627\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"548\" data-imgfileid=\"100017101\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6643c134&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVZnf91jTgHcvKHfIjCDfwOl9f7uK6QToBTPWBuwWTiajkkwzDrBsHFIDs93lr3DCSJCkXf7AeiaIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★CKDA项目旨在解决可见光与红外光下的人员重识别问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">跨模态的知识解耦</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">对齐技术</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，该项目实现了在不同光照条件下的人员识别。项目采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">深度学习</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">方法，利用多个数据集进行训练和测试，提升了模型在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态环境</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">下的识别准确性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ckda\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ckda</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Nemotron-Orchestrator</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32314814814814813\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"376\" data-imgfileid=\"100017100\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3c19685&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVZnf91jTgHcvKHfIjCDfwejC86k0iaqfY5fcGiauLMQyJwv96LvIa7RdlDu38VjDT5r0rPRqXFqnA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Nemotron-Orchestrator-8B是一个先进的8B参数协调模型，旨在通过协调多种专家模型和工具来解决复杂的多轮Agent任务。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">在Humanity's Last Exam (HLE)基准测试中，该模型以37.1%的得分超越了GPT-5（35.1%），并且效率提高了约2.5倍。该模型仅用于研究和开发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nemotron-orchestrator\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nemotron-orchestrator</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总并简要介绍了六个最新的 AI 项目，涵盖基座模型 K2-V2-Instruct、多模态推理模型 Apriel-1.5、视频生成框架 LightX2V、情感支持评估框架 ETrajEval、人员重识别项目 CKDA 以及多专家协调模型 Nemotron-Orchestrator。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总并简要介绍了六个最新的 AI 项目，涵盖基座模型 K2-V2-Instruct、多模态推理模型 Apriel-1.5、视频生成框架 LightX2V、情感支持评估框架 ETrajEval、人员重识别项目 CKDA 以及多专家协调模型 Nemotron-Orchestrator。",
